
Requirements : 
- libxml2
- google sparse hash available at http://code.google.com/p/google-sparsehash/


Instructions to build openpivot executable

- create directory to build it, e.g <debug>
- copy conf.sh into <debug>
- from openpivot root directory, first run autoreconf
- if autoreconf says something, then runs the command suggested in the output
- go to <debug>, edit, conf.sh and replace paths of libxml2 and google sparse by appropriate ones

- run : sh conf.sh
- make

You can go to example/ to test on small data set and run : ../debug/src configsample.xml sampledata.csv output.csv
